<p>This is my last post in partnership with <a href="http://www.bosswatches.co.uk/%20">Boss Orange Watches</a> and I wanted to share with you guys how I decided to style the New York timepiece. It was super cold on the day I took the pictures but the watch still stands out because of its larger face underneath the layers of clothing and looks great with a more casual outfit to wear around town. I chose my <a href="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/time-to-style/#more-3268" class="more-link">&#8230;</a></p>
