<p>We&#8217;re now nearly a week away from Christmas and it&#8217;s around the time where I start to panic about what presents I&#8217;m going to buy my family and friends. So I thought I would put together a gift guide for you filled with some of the things I&#8217;ve picked up this year which I think would make great presents.</p>
<p>&#8211;  <a href="http://steveb.me/1uPw8lT" target="_blank">The Outsiders</a> is an awesome coffee table book filled with some of the most innovative outdoor brands at the moment; great for anyone who loves adventure, design or has a new <a href="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/christmas-gift-ideas/#more-3304" class="more-link">&#8230;</a></p>
