              <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3239" src="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/steve_booker_pemberton_music_festival_canada_1.jpg" alt="steve_booker_pemberton_music_festival_canada_1" width="814" height="543" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3240" src="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/steve_booker_pemberton_music_festival_canada_2.jpg" alt="steve_booker_pemberton_music_festival_canada_2" width="814" height="543" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3241" src="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/steve_booker_pemberton_music_festival_canada_3.jpg" alt="steve_booker_pemberton_music_festival_canada_3" width="814" height="543" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3242" src="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/steve_booker_pemberton_music_festival_canada_4.jpg" alt="steve_booker_pemberton_music_festival_canada_4" width="814" height="543" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3243" src="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/steve_booker_pemberton_music_festival_canada_5.jpg" alt="steve_booker_pemberton_music_festival_canada_5" width="814" height="543" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3244" src="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/steve_booker_pemberton_music_festival_canada_6.jpg" alt="steve_booker_pemberton_music_festival_canada_6" width="814" height="543" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3245" src="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/steve_booker_pemberton_music_festival_canada_7.jpg" alt="steve_booker_pemberton_music_festival_canada_7" width="814" height="543" />
<p>After being at home for the last few weeks I&#8217;ve had a chance to reflect on my recent travelling experiences. One of my favourite memories from the last few months was attending Pemberton Music Festival; it was like no other festival I&#8217;ve been to and the idyllic scenery that surrounds the grounds is awesome! It has a really great atmosphere and you can tell everyone who goes is <a href="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/pemberton-music-festival/#more-3237" class="more-link">&#8230;</a></p>
